text:
How likely is a Type I Error?



\[
\begin{align}
  P(\text{Type I Error})
    &= \class{fragment}{P(\text{reject } H_0 \mid H_0 \text{ is true})} \\[3px]
    &\class{fragment}{{} = P(Z \geq z_\alpha \mid} \class{fragment}{Z \sim N(0,1))}       \\[3px]
    &\class{fragment}{{} = \alpha}
\end{align}
\]
